data.text: @DorkSideOForce @graigs43 It completely and single handedly ruined my 40 years of love for Star Wars. I even loved both cartoon series.  Even they captured the essence of Star Wars.  The TLJ was a  complete disgrace to the entire franchise.  Even Solo was awesome. I'm confused why it bothers me so much.

@DorkSideOForce @graigs43 Much like in different Spiderman or Batman movies TLJ was a completely different altetnate universe setting.  I hate that I hate the TLJ so much. Rhian did such a horrible job portraying this epic story.  How could "The Force Awakens" be so incredible and "TLJ" BE SO BAD?  SMH.🤔
